339
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:05,920
Strýko Mo, nechcete snáď aj s riaditeľom,

340
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:08,490
aby som sa stala schopnou dedičkou?

341
00:18:08,490 --> 00:18:10,000
Chcela by som,

342
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,630
