399
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,560
Dobre.

400
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,810
Prinesiem vodu.

401
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:52,840
Dedko.

402
00:20:54,870 --> 00:20:56,110
Tu, pozor.

403
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:58,390
Voda.

404
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:06,300
Ako sa cítiš?

405
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:10,770
Už dobre.
O chvíľu budem v pohode.

406
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:16,600
