409
00:21:31,630 --> 00:21:33,760
Neviem, či to zvládne.

410
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:37,680
Hrozne ma to vydesilo.
Povedala som snáď niečo zle?

411
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:41,970
